Title: Head Cheese
Plot: Nancy must deal with the aftermath of Shane's exploits, her Ayahuasca trip, and more confrontation with Guillermo. Celia's struggles with her rehab partner, Barry, force her to find a new rehab facility. Doug and Maria's relationship quickly goes south and they both turn to Andy for help. Meanwhile, Silas's "sandwich" business has grown too big, forcing him to turn to Nancy for help.
Writer: Roberto Benabib, Rolin Jones, Matthew Salsberg
GuestStars: Demian Bichir, Julie Bowen, Guillermo Diaz, Bob Odenkirk, Maulik Pancholy
